name: Office Backrooms
description:
What happens when you NoClip out of reality? 

Well in this case, NoClip out of your office...

you get stuck in an endless procedurally generated rooms, trying to find your way out. Or in this case, find 5 specific papers.

Dont worry, take your time. As long as you dont hear any sounds.

because if you do, God save you, it has heard you too.

Note: Please read README file before opening.

Thank uou
